      <title>极右翼选举失败后德国保守党民调支持率下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/merz-s-conservatives-drop-2-points-after-controversial-afd-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新的民意调查显示，德国中右翼、由弗里德里希·梅尔茨领导的联盟党支持率下降，而绿党和两个较小的极左翼政党的支持率则有所上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/merz-s-conservatives-drop-2-points-after-controversial-afd-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 13:26:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙计划缩短工作周以改善工作与生活的平衡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/spanish-government-plans-to-cut-weekly-working-hours-to-37-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙政府达成协议，将每周工作时间从 40 小时减少至 37.5 小时，因为首相佩德罗·桑切斯 (Pedro Sanchez) 试图利用社会政策，但议会支持率却很低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/spanish-government-plans-to-cut-weekly-working-hours-to-37-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:27:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国外长斯塔默在特朗普格陵兰争议中迟迟支持丹麦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/uk-s-starmer-belatedly-backs-denmark-in-trump-greenland-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相的发言人表示，英国首相基尔·斯塔默支持丹麦对格陵兰岛的主权，此前美国总统唐纳德·特朗普重申了美国获得北极岛屿的意图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/uk-s-starmer-belatedly-backs-denmark-in-trump-greenland-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:13:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩洛哥工会呼吁十年来首次因工资问题举行总罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/morocco-unions-call-first-general-strike-in-decade-on-wage-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩洛哥最大的劳工团体呼吁进行近十年来首次全国性罢工，以迫使总理阿齐兹·阿汉努赫恢复工资谈判并撤销改革该国不完善的养老金制度的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/morocco-unions-call-first-general-strike-in-decade-on-wage-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平对特朗普关税的谨慎回应表明中国将面临更多损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/xi-s-careful-reply-to-trump-tariffs-shows-china-has-more-to-lose</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新一轮中美贸易战的首轮攻势明确表明，习近平采取了比唐纳德·特朗普第一任期期间更为谨慎的态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/xi-s-careful-reply-to-trump-tariffs-shows-china-has-more-to-lose</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 12:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国下令切断缅甸电力以打击诈骗中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/thailand-mulls-cutting-power-to-myanmar-in-blow-to-scam-centers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继中国演员被贩卖事件引起泰国边境犯罪活动的关注后，泰国将切断缅甸部分涉嫌进行网络诈骗活动的地区的电力、互联网和石油供应，加大打击力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/thailand-mulls-cutting-power-to-myanmar-in-blow-to-scam-centers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 09:23:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡准备与特朗普会面，权力仍未稳固</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/netanyahu-readies-trump-white-house-meeting-with-gaza-ceasefire-at-crucial-stage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和本杰明·内塔尼亚胡周二的会谈将决定以色列与哈马斯战争的进程，并可能决定总理继续执政的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/netanyahu-readies-trump-white-house-meeting-with-gaza-ceasefire-at-crucial-stage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 07:02:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼通过法律设立 610 亿美元投资机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/indonesia-passes-law-to-create-61-billion-investment-agency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚修改了管理东南亚国家强大国有企业的法律，为成立一个管理数十亿美元国有资产的新机构奠定了法律基础，同时寻求在国内和潜在的海外投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/indonesia-passes-law-to-create-61-billion-investment-agency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 03:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命宽带扩张计划批评者监督该计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-tap-critic-of-biden-broadband-plan-to-oversee-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据三位知情人士透露，特朗普政府选择了前总统乔·拜登 425 亿美元宽带融资计划的反对者来监督该计划，这使其方向受到质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-tap-critic-of-biden-broadband-plan-to-oversee-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 01:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言惩罚南非的征地法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-pledges-to-cut-aid-to-south-africa-over-land-expropriation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，由于南非的新土地征用法，美国将停止未来对南非的所有资助。兰特下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-pledges-to-cut-aid-to-south-africa-over-land-expropriation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:58:39 GMT</pubDate>
